node.text:
Shop Googan Baits jr series right now @googansquad .com. Enter code LFG for discount 

My first cast with @googanbaits JR trench hog produced some magnums. I filmed this exactly a year ago this week on my phone while testing out some first runs of the jr series. They are outstanding action for the smaller profile! #googan #bassfishing #fall #bigbass

node.title: First casts with JR. Googan Baits - MONDOS!

node.text: Doing some custom wood work to complete the wall of the fish cave where fish mounts and other cool fishing freak stuff will go. You can follow along for the full project on me and OSG’s family channel. LAKE LIFE FAMILY on YouTube. I’ve been excited for this project since we moved in and it’s going well!
